%% Diagram: useSyncExternalStore tearing prevention
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Store as "External store"
    participant React as "React (concurrent renderer)"
    participant Comp1 as "Component A"
    participant Comp2 as "Component B"

    Note over React: Concurrent render begins (interruptible)
    React->>Comp1: Render
    Comp1->>Store: getSnapshot() returns v1
    Note over Store: External mutation: v1 -> v2
    React->>Comp2: Render (paused tasks resume)
    Comp2->>Store: getSnapshot() returns v2
    Note over React: Pre-commit consistency check<br/>useSyncExternalStore re-reads snapshot
    React->>Store: getSnapshot() returns v2
    Note over React: v2 != snapshot read by Comp1<br/>Tearing detected
    React->>React: Restart render synchronously with v2
    React->>Comp1: Re-render with v2
    React->>Comp2: Re-render with v2
    React->>React: Commit (all components see v2)
